      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TIME OF DESIGN (1) has a strong overall record having four wins and eight places from 15 starts including a last start success (19.70) over 342m at this track. Tends to go well on this box draw. Drawn the rails and rates a key runner. ZING MATILDA (2) had a tricky draw last time and although midfield in fifth wasn't far away finishing 2.75 lengths from the winner (20.40). Solid record here at the distance winning six races. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings five times from six attempts. A forward showing wouldn't surprise. SHARPEN UP (4) was game in defeat off a low draw at the latest outing, finishing second and beaten 2 lengths (20.09) behind Zinfandel Emma at this track. The form from his last run stacks up well. Overdue and gets his chance. ELEGANT FLINT (8) cannot be written off despite a miss here at his latest outing.",
